"create a quiz <events/track-add-quiz>` specific to the topic related to that "
"particular track."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_tracks.rst:39
msgid ""
"Once all desired settings have been enabled, be sure to click "
"the :guilabel:`Save` button in the upper-left corner of "
"the :guilabel:`Settings` page."
msgstr ""

