#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_tracks.rst:51
msgid ""
"Once on the desired event form, click into the :guilabel:`Tracks` smart "
"button at the top of the form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_tracks.rst:55
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Tracks` smart button is not readily available, click "
"the :guilabel:`More` :icon:`fa-sort-desc` drop-down menu to reveal hidden "
"smart buttons. Then, click :guilabel:`Tracks` from the resulting drop-down "
