msgstr "Odoo इवेंट ऐप्लिकेशन में किसी इवेंट के लिए टिपिकल इवेंट ट्रैक पेज।"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_tracks.rst:67
msgid ""
"The tracks are presented in a default :icon:`oi-view-"
"kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)` view, but there is also the option to view "
