"can be edited, if needed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/event_tracks.rst:80
msgid ""
"To edit a stage, hover over the stage name, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Settings)` icon, and select :guilabel:`Edit` from the "
"resulting drop-down menu."
