"to :menuselection:`Events app --> Registration Desk`, and selecting "
"the :guilabel:`Select Attendee` option."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/registration_desk.rst:51
msgid ""
"Odoo reveals an :guilabel:`Attendees` page, with all the attendees for every "
"event in the database, in a default :icon:`oi-view-"
"kanban` :guilabel:`Kanban` view."
